name: Mdtocs
body:
### Welcome to MDTOCS

The finest tables of contents for your markdown files.

```

generated by [mtdocs](http://mdtocs.rsb.io/)

- [My Cool Document](#my-cool-document)
\t- [Subheading](#subheading)
\t- [With Underlined subheader](#with-underlined-subheader)
\t\t- [And Subsubheadings](#and-subsubheadings)

#My Cool Document

Is a document

##Subheading

Subheadings are key to nirvana

With Underlined subheader
-------------------------

And information

###And Subsubheadings

The end, dude.
```
